name: ExtendRenewalDateResponse
desc: A response that indicates whether the renewal-date extension succeeded and related details.

items.name: effectiveDate
items.desc: The date that the successful subscription-renewal extension begins.

items.name: originalTransactionId
items.desc: The original transaction identifier of the subscription that experienced a service interruption.

items.name: success
items.desc: A Boolean value that indicates whether the subscription-renewal-date extension succeeded.

items.name: webOrderLineItemId
items.desc: A unique ID that identifies subscription-purchase events including subscription renewals, across devices.
